# Architecture: business vs presentation

Canonical: `/.claude/rules/10-architecture.md`

Follow the required 3-layer pattern for **any** business logic:

1. `lib/<namespace>/` (pure/testable business logic)
2. `hooks/` (React orchestration)
3. UI component (render view state: loading/error/success)

